{"tid":693013,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"對屋企人嘅辱罵，應該俾咩反應？","createTime":"2018-06-07T06:23:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-07T14:33:20.000Z","uid":162853,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"43a351d9828a9e39d081a84c2a6237695104ac1b","tid":693013,"uid":162853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T06:23:40.000Z","msg":"自問由細到大都係乖嗰type 成績ok<br />\n大學grad左就已經有做野 <br />\n因為係細公司 所以份工平時係喺屋企做 一星期有兩日返去開會<br />\n聽落好似幾輕鬆 其實d野都係趕住嚟做 成日做到半夜<br />\n咁做到攰 日頭嘅時間就想休息下都好正常啫<br />\n但屋企人成日覺得我係好撚得閒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有解釋過 但佢哋覺得我搵籍口<br />\n又覺得我份工工作模式古怪 總之就唔正經<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日屌鳩我話唔理屋企d嘢又唔幫手做家務<br />\n一日到黑懶懶閒 垃圾無撚用乞米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有好多踩人嘅說話費事講<br />\n<br />\n唉 都唔知可以點<br />\n有無巴絲屋企人都係咁&ldquo;盟塞&rdquo;？<br />\n對住佢哋真係唔想講嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a861ee07e0f2ef8f16716b577bdaa9f245675c","tid":693013,"uid":155818,"like":3,"dislike":14,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T06:25:51.000Z","msg":"咁你真係好得閒嘛"},{"pid":"2fddd6e7fdd3c58699f0b9a247c1abdf540b37a0","tid":693013,"uid":113335,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T06:26:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://adultdeepfakes.com/v324939\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fadultdeepfakes.com%2Fv324939&d=PnqHV%2BUNtOls%2FEpEQrMap54%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=2309c930\" target=\"_blank\">https://adultdeepfakes.com/v324939</a>"},{"pid":"df19b42d9b7352e102b5d9e979d189c6f373d268","tid":693013,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T06:26:25.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多"},{"pid":"e1675ee510f4d465f92992bedc998807a12bbffc","tid":693013,"uid":74622,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-07T06:27:42.000Z","msg":"搵到錢比到家用仲會比說話你聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmo